;FVar(10) = General HP
;FVar(11) = Gas Strength (HP)
;FVar(12) = Gas Build Rate

;Gas Strength increases by Gas Build Rate every frame
;Gas Build Rate slowly increases up to 0.25 (0.001)
;Gas Strength decreases by 100% more than the damage that was taken
;Gas Build Rate decreases by damage taken *0.1
;If Gas Build Rate goes negative, Gas Strength stop increasing
;Lowest Gas Build Rate can become is -2
;Gas is Lv.X, where X is +1 for every 1000 HP the Gas Stength has
;General loses HP equal to (0.01*Gas Lv) every frame

;========================================
;Gas/Police Chief Life Code Start
;========================================

;Gas Build Rate increase
[State 21627, VarAdd]
