;Mona sets root, Var(27) to -3 and goes to this state
;Root detects var(27) is set to -3, and then sets var(27) to either -1 or -2 depending on Lisa's position to Mona
;Lisa detects root, var(27) change to either -1 or -2, and goes to walk state (21845)
;When Lisa is behind Mona (root, FVar(22) < -5), Lisa stops, the hitoverride is disabled (if active), and Mona activates her hitdef.

;If Mona somehow gets hit before Lisa reaches her, set root, Var(27) to 30. Lisa leaves walk state to normal stand state

